text: Stanislau Hladchenko () (born 14 September 1994) is a Belarusian male freestyle skier. He competed in the men's aerials event during the 2018 Winter Olympics. == References == Category:1994 births Category:Living people Category:Belarusian male freestyle skiers Category:Freestyle skiers at the 2018 Winter Olympics Category:Olympic freestyle skiers of Belarus Category:Sportspeople from Minsk
